name: Hentai Woman
description:
With 3d puzzle you will feel comfortable and enjoy yourself.

You will experience the puzzle experience with better graphics with 3 dimensions much better.

There are different characters and different sections.

With Administrator mode you can open the characters that can be seen in sections.

In Administrator mode, you can display the characters with the ( f ) key.

There are also more than 100 achievements in the game.
